Example
The greater-than symbol followed by a space (> ) represents the user input. Note that it's not part of the input.

Enter the number of rows:
> 7
Enter the number of seats in each row:
> 7

1. Show the seats
2. Buy a ticket
0. Exit
> 1

Cinema:
  1 2 3 4 5 6 7
1 S S S S S S S
2 S S S S S S S
3 S S S S S S S
4 S S S S S S S
5 S S S S S S S
6 S S S S S S S
7 S S S S S S S

1. Show the seats
2. Buy a ticket
0. Exit
> 2

